config SENSOR_MODULE_HUMID_DELTA_INT
	int "Variation in humidity required to register a measurement. Integer part."
	default 1
	help
		Required difference in humidity to register a new measurement.
		Unit is relative humidity represented as a percentage. 
		Set this and the decimal part to 0 to always register the latest measurement.

config SENSOR_MODULE_HUMID_DELTA_DEC
	int "Variation in humidity required to register a measurement. Decimal part."
	default 0
	help
		Required difference in humidity to register a new measurement.
		Unit is decimal part of relative humidity represented as a percentage. 
		Divide by 1E6 to get actual decimal value. 
		Set this and the integer part to 0 to always register the latest measurement.

config SENSOR_MODULE_GAS_RES_DELAY
