config SENSOR_MODULE_GAS_RES_DELTA
	int "Variation in gas resistance required to register a measurement."
	default 1000
	help
		Required difference in gas resistance to register a new measurement.
		Unit is Ohm. 
		Set this to 0 to always register the latest measurement.

